{"title":"列车在飞奔","authors":["黎之"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":4,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"列车在飞奔\t黎之"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩色的原野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩色的云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩色的道路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列车在飞奔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉开窗帘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看窗外是什么时辰："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方是红霞朵朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞起了红日一轮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃枝抹红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳条涂金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是一派大好春色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是一个美妙的早晨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地春光美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车外景色新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回头看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车内的春色更动人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一位小伙子要到矿山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一位姑娘要到农村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许是车上初逢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们却谈得那样起劲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“高山和平原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有无尽的宝藏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要去取那金钥匙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开这宝库的大门。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“肥沃的土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正等待着播种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要用双手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把大地耕耘。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里话音未落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里笑声又闻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一对老战友车上巧遇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把别后的经历谈论。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我踏遍祖国的土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为的是把地下宝藏探寻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这事儿真不容易，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比当年‘捉舌头’还难几分。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我就要到国外去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接触陌生的工作陌生的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在正在当小学生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个字一个字学习外文。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“老行当用不上啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切得要从头学起。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不，走到天涯海角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也丢不了咱们的传家宝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——革命精神！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这儿正在热烈地谈话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边发生了“纠纷”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位是乘务员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位是解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个人你夺我抢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争着打扫车厢里的灰尘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我来吧，你们休息一下。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不，还是让我干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是我们的本分。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们争执不下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一对孩子抢走了扫帚和抹布："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“叔叔、阿姨别争了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这活儿还是让给俺红领巾。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处是歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满车是欢欣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车厢显得窄小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"容不下这热情的气氛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车轮显得太慢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比不过一颗颗飞腾的心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远方在把人们召唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的事业在把人们吸引，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进的列车啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更快地转动你的车轮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着远方，向着太阳飞奔！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}